{"id": "1509005902953451590", "channel_id": "1509005902953451590", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437420114826756117", "author_name": "lingyujiling", "author_bot": false, "content": "课题命轮奖励明明写着可以选择五枚流明之芯，这版本却只能从三个课题命轮中选择。如果还像以前一样溢出的命轮可以变成灵核碎片也就算了，现在你领取了强制转换成命轮自选碎片，那对于三个命轮全部+12的玩家来说奖励岂不是从5抽缩水到了3抽，应用场景从通用抽限制为只能换命轮。这难道不是实打实地在损害玩家利益吗？\n\n\nThe reward of the project life wheel clearly says that you can choose five rumen cores, but this version can only choose from three project life wheels. If the overflowing life wheel can be turned into spiritual core fragments as before, it's okay. Now that you have received the forced conversion into life wheel self-selected fragments, isn't the reward for all +12 players in the three life wheels from 5 draws to 3 draws? The application scenario is limited from general draw to only changing the life wheel. Isn't this really harming the interests of players?", "timestamp": "2026-05-27T01:30:43.238000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💀", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}, {"emoji": "😭", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1509005903494643874", "filename": "IMG_4335.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1044089, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1509005902953451590/1509005903494643874/IMG_4335.png?ex=6a184383&is=6a16f203&hm=bc0ae43330e2c53f02307cb99568caa35a57e0ae1f4b13cb1ffab4a767c6e17d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1509005902953451590", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」课题奖励暗改是否又是你猫小巧思的一环", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"], "is_thread_starter": true}
